{"tid":1473601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我重組左8月13號五點後既航班資料，發現取消既只有廿三班，有齊數據","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:51:33.000Z","uid":20414,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1c242f9b5fcbb9ea8e1f987c1ebaa0f8d8e685","tid":1473601,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"當日機場運作因為集會導致不暢順，但五時之前航班仍然正常。約五時廿分機管局宣布關關所有櫃位同所有離港航班取消。<br />\n從唔同渠道我拎左幾個時段既顯示屏圖片，再對比 Google 同 flight radar 數據，發現由六點開始佢地將航班轉到 &quot;Cancelled&quot; ，但臨近起飛前五十分鐘，航班狀況會改為&quot;準備登機中&quot; 。<br />\n此舉會導致幾個問題<br />\n1）前線抗爭者誤以為所有航班取消因此阻礙旅客入閘，但旅客因為手持有效登機證，所以急於衝關導致衝突<br />\n2）未 check in 的乘客會因應機管局訊息而選擇不前往機場，但航班因為準時起飛，佢地會變成 No Show。如果重新訂位，誰負責費用？<br />\n3）對外宣稱大量航班取消，但明顯地1730到0000在T1 check in 而取消既航班只有二十三班 （中國國航不能算入因為佢地自己取消香港航班）<br />\n<br />\n很想各傳媒幫忙跟進，作為公營機構既機管局， 為何挑起旅客和示威者間嘅紛爭？<br />\n<br />\n＃五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"817d0f7c2ccebb91d963b8b47d30129fb8428e91","tid":1473601,"uid":20414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFc0vP3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFc0vP3.jpg&h=ace58122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtCWOBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtCWOBG.jpg&h=bba1f7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYZRCu0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYZRCu0.jpg&h=a12e39bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b7b1901fc76df5f78f2e1dea6e3d661061a5a40","tid":1473601,"uid":20414,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWh7Vg5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWh7Vg5.jpg&h=3d8d6f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxfQS3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpxfQS3P.jpg&h